FBIS3-54681 "drsov001_r_94001" FBIS-SOV-94-001 Document Type:Daily Report 3 Jan 1994 Azerbaijan Aliyev Invited To Visit Turkey, Iran NC0201190094 Baku Radio Baku Network in Azeri 1700 GMT 2 Jan 94 NC0201190094 Baku Radio Baku Network Language: Azeri Article Type:BFN [Text] The Azerbaijan Presidential Press Service has disclosed that President Hashemi-Rafsanjani has conveyed a letter to President Geydar Aliyev that focused significant attention on the need to strengthen friendship and cooperation between Azerbaijan and Iran. Taking that into consideration, President Hashemi-Rafsanjani invited President Aliyev to visit Iran at a convenient time. It will be recalled that President Suleyman Demirel invited President Aliyev to visit Turkey a day before President Hashemi-Rafsanjani's invitation was received.
